rows.label: qst006601_msg0001
rows.name:
I haven't eaten a proper meal in
four whole days!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0002
rows.name:
Surely you can spare a little grub
for poor old me?!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0004
rows.name:
We worked hard to get our hands
on these rations ourselves!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0005
rows.name: I can't just hand them over!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0006
rows.name:
What did you say?! That does it,
I'm taking them by force-

rows.label: qst006601_msg0007
rows.name:
Trying to assault an unarmed woman?
Have you no shame?!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0009
rows.name:
You're bothering these people.
If you leave quietly, we won't hurt you.

rows.label: qst006601_msg0010
rows.name:
Wh-what do you know about my
troubles?! Don't talk like you're
oh so superior!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0011
rows.name:
Step back, you two.
This won't take long.
